Class HashMappedAdviceEffectuation

java.lang.Object
  lu.uni.geko.weaver.HashMappedAdviceEffectuation
All Implemented Interfaces:
AdviceEffectuation
public class HashMappedAdviceEffectuation
extends Object
implements AdviceEffectuation

An implementation of the convenience representation (or proxy) of an AdviceEffectuation that encapsulates the data needed during the effectuation of an advice .


Attention: The collections returned by this implementation are backed up. Changing the returned collections will change collections of this implementation.
